<div class="c24"><span class="c16">10.</span> <span class="c16">《佛教上道教》，久保田量远著， 《东洋文化史大系(隋唐の盛世)》<span>   </span></span></div>
<div class="c24"><span class="c16">11.</span><span class="c16">《道藏にフぃての一管见》，福井康顺著，《东洋思想研究》第三 <span>  </span></span></div>
<div class="c24"><span class="c16">12.</span><span class="c16">《道教の实态》、吉冈义丰编著<span>  </span></span></div>
<div class="c24"><span class="c16">13.</span><span class="c16">《道教思想》，幸田露伴著，《露伴全集》第18卷<span>  </span></span></div>
<div class="c24"><span class="c16">14.</span><span class="c16">《中国目录学史》，姚名达编<span>  </span></span></div>
<div class="c24"><span class="c16">15.</span><span class="c16">《南宗初河北新道教考》，陈垣著<span>   </span></span></div>
<div class="c24"><span class="c16">16.</span><span class="c16">《老庄の思想と道教》，小柳司气太著<span>  </span></span></div>
